{"tid":1961571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方接報昨於炮台山塗鴉黑點埋伏 拘捕五名女子 一人腳部受傷送院","createTime":"2020-04-07T01:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T02:34:41.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc28c782437a1a9f7dd1e8f78353bd329222c3f","tid":1961571,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:20:35.000Z","msg":"炮台山行人天橋被塗鴉警方拘捕五名女子<br />\n07.04.2020 07:54<br />\n<br />\n警方在炮台山拘捕五名年齡20歲多女子，涉嫌刑事毀壞及藏有工具可作非法用途。警方早前接報，英皇道近福元街一條行人天橋被人噴上油漆，深夜11時許派員在附近埋伏，發現五名女子形跡可疑，上前截查，檢獲四支噴漆及一對膠手套，懷疑有人用噴漆塗鴉。期間一對姊妹逃走，跌傷腳部送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279179&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279179%26csid%3D261_341&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=ff937e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279179&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"69b90c54de671f443b99a5ee1ea57c6e6d86b297","tid":1961571,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:23:53.000Z","msg":"姐係9拉"},{"pid":"583304995e03ddd34d6cd5cbb96d3e4f7b3fa29d","tid":1961571,"uid":131157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rUC2kXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrUC2kXW.jpg&h=c28f36b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkHxJbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkHxJbh.jpg&h=b9ab3f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rg4W9Ri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRg4W9Ri.jpg&h=a117d9a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07929d468229b88f95648b77bdc115dac966a821","tid":1961571,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"唔畀女人做裝修<img src=\"/assets